msgid ""
"This device contains a valid firmware, but EEPROM is invalid.\n"
"Probably the device has not been initialised, or the EEPROM has been "
"erased.\n"
"Please correctly initialise the device and try again!"
msgstr ""
"該設備包含有效的固件，但EEPROM無效。 \n"
" 可能尚未初始化該設備，或者已經刪除了EEPROM。 \n"
" 請正確初始化設備，然後重試！!"
